Struct `CoinDecimalsRegistered` appears to be a token/asset but has both `copy` and `drop` abilities. This enables infinite duplication. Assets should only have `key` and `store`. See: https://www.mirageaudits.com/blog/sui-move-ability-security-mistakes
Functions should not be both `public` and `entry`; remove one of the modifiers
